Plug in
  • Simple setup — Just power on this plug, and say to Echo “Alexa, discover devices”, Your Echo device will automatically detect and set up those smart plugs. No App required for the pairing process.
  • You can control lights, fans and appliances with your voice and in the Alexa App — remote control, group control, schedule, timer, rename and other functions.
  • Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) Mesh plug-to-plug connection helps intelligently eliminate signal dead zones — connect multiple plugs to extend your voice control capabilities beyond signal dead zones, each BLE Mesh plug acts as its own hub beyond the Echo.
  • YNF Smart Plug is optimized for simple setup and exclusive use with Alexa — YNF Smart Plug does not support other Apps or other voice assistants.
  • Network connection requires Echo, a range of Echo can connect seamlessly to the YNF smart plug via BLE Mesh— Echo (2nd Gen and newer), Echo Dot (2nd Gen and newer), Echo Plus, Echo Show, Echo Studio, and more. (Only the 1st Gen Echo and 1st Echo Dot are not supported)

Product description

Voice Control

Free up your hands by using simple voice commands with Echo.

Remote Control

Effortlessly manage your connected appliances anytime, anywhere.(Echo is required)

Auto Reconnection

Wider range control via mesh transmission between Bluetooth plugs.

Schedule Your Home

Save energy and automate your life with custom scheduling and timers

Count Down Timer

Set a timer for your connected appliance to automatically turn off when the time runs out.

Group Control

Group your plug with other devices to turn them all on or off with one click.

Support both 2.4G or 5G

YNF smart plug connects to Alexa Echo via BLE Mesh, regardless of 2.4Ghz and 5Ghz WiFi networks.

Security Protection

YNF uses Fire resistant 1383°F ABS material and high-quality chips and provide overload protection to ensure the safety of family members.

Don't Slow down Your WiFi

Network connection is through the Alexa Echo, and not directly connected to the WiFi network.

Security and privacy

Enjoy ultimate privacy with Mesh smart plug. No other cloud, no registration, and no data tracking.

Simple Set Up

With Bluetooth simple setup, you can make your home smart in a snap. All you need is the Alexa app or Echo to control your outlet from anywhere.

We want you to know：

  • This is a Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) Mesh smart plug,network connection requires Alexa Echo, and the smart plug connects to Alexa Echo via BLE Mesh.
  • Check that your paired plug is within 30 ft (9 m) of your Alexa Echo. (if there is an indoor barrier, the distance cannot exceed 10 ft).
  • Make sure the Echo is online before setting up the smart plug.Set the plugs one by one, and do not pair multiple plugs at the same time.
  • YNF Smart Plug is optimized for simple setup and exclusive use with Alexa, and it does not support other Apps or other voice assistants. it isn't compatible with Smart Life, Homekit, Google home and SmartThings.

      Here’s a brief rundown of my experience:

      Pros:

      Easy Setup: The setup was incredibly straightforward. I just powered on the plug and asked Alexa to discover devices. It took less than a minute, and I didn’t need to use any additional apps.
      Reliable Performance: I’ve been using these smart plugs for a few weeks, and they have consistently performed well. They respond instantly to voice commands and have had no connection issues.
      Versatile Control: The ability to control devices through voice commands or the Alexa app is convenient. I’ve set up schedules and timers for my lights, which has been a nice addition to my daily routine.
      Mesh Networking: The Bluetooth Mesh feature is fantastic. It allows me to extend the range of my smart home network and eliminates dead zones in my house, which is a huge plus.
      Cons:

      Alexa-Only Compatibility: The only limitation is that these plugs work exclusively with Alexa, so they might not be suitable for users who rely on other smart home platforms.
      Overall, these YNF Smart Plugs have been a great addition to my home. They offer reliable performance, easy setup, and convenient control options, making them well worth the investment. If you’re an Alexa user looking for a simple and effective way to manage your devices, these smart plugs are a solid choice.

      I was very happy with the Kasa Smart plug I had but it's shape became an issue. It was plugged directly into the outlet behind our full size bed. When we added additional devices and got a king bed that sits higher, we got an outlet extender that was on the larger side.... See more
      I was very happy with the Kasa Smart plug I had but it's shape became an issue. It was plugged directly into the outlet behind our full size bed. When we added additional devices and got a king bed that sits higher, we got an outlet extender that was on the larger side. The outlets on it swivel to allow them to be on the front or side. Neither option worked well for the rectangular kasa charger. It was too wide for the front and too long for the side option. This smaller, round charger was the perfect solution. When swiveled to the side, this smart plug has plenty of room to sit between the wall and the box spring. It connected easily with my Alexa app. I have one lamp plugged into it and one plugged into the kasa lamp across the room. There are no issues with the both plugs being used in the same room group in Alexa. I would buy again if I need another round plug in the future.
